Additionally, you can just swap the values.

```java
&lt;T&gt; void transpose(T[][] a) {
    int m = a.length, n = a[0].length;
    T t;
    for (int i = 0, j; i &lt; m; i++)
        for (j = i + 1; j &lt; n; j++) {
            t = a[i][j];
            a[i][j] = a[j][i];
            a[j][i] = t;
        }
}
```

